{"tid":1366182,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"同條女扑完嘢覺得好委屈","createTime":"2019-07-26T01:27:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T01:54:46.000Z","uid":290425,"like":3,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"4ebeb47690dcf32a85b872671c6d9bbf44793a34","tid":1366182,"uid":290425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T01:27:08.000Z","msg":"［好委屈］上女友屋企扑嘢，佢落街幫我買左套，扑完之後佢慣幫我除套掉落佢床邊個垃圾桶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但之後我佢竟然放係垃圾桶一晚唔記得清！咁我梗係話佢好噁心，佢仲要嬲豬，話幫我做咁多嘢我so晒仲要話佢！各位巴絲話啱唔啱啦，佢無so架？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：40幾仲有心有力，條女今年都29，小肥，但話每次扑都好enjoy，仲話我_到佢好入，點解仲可以話我so晒，佢無so架？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家d港女真係堅難頂"},{"pid":"63ef96af7ea77dcdd9f07985dfa88235d59d98b9","tid":1366182,"uid":161209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T01:34:15.000Z","msg":"咁嫌棄人嘅咪唔好同人一齊囉 唔好哂人時間 渣男<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"369027bce26f2b7948cbb991e5cda195fe391c5a","tid":1366182,"uid":219128,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T01:35:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fKt8c1k.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfKt8c1k.png&h=3d86918c&s={SIZ